We are creating a show, it is largely inspired by the Survivor show. Two teams will be marooned on an island. The characters will go through challenges, voting each other off of the island.

16 competitors, they are castaways, marooned on an island in Costa Rica territory. The names of the tribes: Fugaz Tribe (purple color is their theme), and Oxigeno Tribe (red color is their theme).

The world is basically the human world with a mix of anthropomorphic animal characters.

